Humans

Hunger works 0.5 faster - pork, lamb, beef equal saturation - fish & everything else saturation is halved their normal.
Water speed is halved - boats works normal.

All villages are infected.
Zombies poison and skeletons cant die under the sun.
Posion spider only.
Mob respawn normal.
